Huntington Beach Public Library Central Branch offers a seed lending program

Post Date:02/15/2016 11:00 AM

The Huntington Beach Public Library, 7111 Talbert Ave, HB, CA 92648, is partnering with Garden Pool and is offering a seed lending program. The Seed Library is stored in a hand-crafted card catalog on the first floor of the Central Library.
